<item>
            <title>[LU-4654] sanity test_129: current dir size 12288, previous limit 12288</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4654</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks a lot like &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3909&quot; title=&quot;Interop 2.4.0&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;2.5 failure on test suite sanity test_129: return code 28 received instead of expected 27&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3909&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3909&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, already fixed.  Not sure if this is a new bug or that same old bug popping up again.  Not seen during version interop, as reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3909&quot; title=&quot;Interop 2.4.0&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;2.5 failure on test suite sanity test_129: return code 28 received instead of expected 27&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3909&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3909&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Seems like a high runner blocking tests. maloo reports:&lt;br/&gt;
Failure Rate: 19.00% of last 100 executions &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;all branches&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cf2c124c-9a26-11e3-baa9-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/cf2c124c-9a26-11e3-baa9-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_129 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;current dir size 12288, previous limit 12288&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 129&lt;/p&gt;</description>
